{"tid":1391493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［唔好忘記台灣呢個籌碼］中國暫停所有台灣自遊行簽證！","createTime":"2019-07-31T12:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T02:23:42.000Z","uid":274526,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7c3fbcf91f4c6e31f9aaf64da552c9311c62b5d5","tid":1391493,"uid":274526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:39:25.000Z","msg":"新聞：<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190731&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59881675\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190731%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59881675&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFp2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=4191aaad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190731%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59881675&h=48b864d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190731&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59881675</a><br />\n<br />\n香港呢單嘢，令唔少台灣人看在眼內，民意都向蔡英文轉。而家中共就想「收復失地」，減少自由行拉到台灣經濟，等民眾覺得「中國好」，之後投返國民黨。<br />\n<br />\n所以呢期在海外的朋友，除咗同人講香港，不妨推介多啲外國人去台灣玩！<br />\n<br />\n只要一日香港仲可以係台灣嘅「示範單位」，嚴重影響到民眾選舉意向，一日我哋個籌碼都會多啲！"},{"pid":"3b8d5e5eda58d90371a489dca709b6e771dac27f","tid":1391493,"uid":89392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:45:02.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得係因為中共國內唔夠錢，要搵個藉口堵塞外匯流出嘅管道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"14b977c21c223ce3f31182506d40f1fab0e0fe26","tid":1391493,"uid":76068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:02:32.000Z","msg":"中共停台灣自由行, 想令台灣經濟差, 等生果佬可以用「帶動台灣經濟」為由而當選...到時候自己多人擁護"},{"pid":"e4f3c37f2da31b870c20eb9d9043afdb534fd6c3","tid":1391493,"uid":68746,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:47:49.000Z","msg":"咁做唔係會有反效果咩"},{"pid":"53e4e360dda5a469cda5bb4df4daa25634485e1f","tid":1391493,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:23:42.000Z","msg":"支援台灣！！"}]}